  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BooleanFalsePreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the value is not true.
    BooleanTruePreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the value is true.
    CollectionEmptyPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the collection is not empty.
    CollectionNotEmptyPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the collection is empty.
    JodaTimeEqualOrAfterPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the first value is equal to or after second value.
    JodaTimeEqualPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the first value is equal to second value.
    JodaTimeNotEqualOrAfterPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the first value is not equal to or after second value.
    JodaTimeNotEqualPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the first value is not equal to second value.
    ObjectNotNullPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the value is not null.
    ObjectNullPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the value is not null.
    PreconditionException
    Abstract class for all precondition exceptions.
    StringBlankPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the value is not blank.
    StringNotBlankPreconditionException
    This exception is thrown if the value is blank.
